through our doors today,

00:06:31.070 --> 00:06:35.250
they're essentially
creating relationship space,

00:06:35.250 --> 00:06:37.610
relationship capital,
where if they're

00:06:37.610 --> 00:06:41.360
able to prove their abilities
in a difficult, competitive work

00:06:41.360 --> 00:06:45.140
environment in an elite setting,
that opens the doors for others

00:06:45.140 --> 00:06:46.830
to come behind them.

00:06:46.830 --> 00:06:49.760
And an example, it
wouldn't have been

00:06:49.760 --> 00:06:52.767
