get the bulk of that order.

00:07:05.660 --> 00:07:08.840
That's the problem to solve
for the manager of the desk.

00:07:08.840 --> 00:07:11.291
They look around and
they say, who do I trust?

00:07:11.291 --> 00:07:13.040
Who I do I know is
going to get this done.

00:07:13.040 --> 00:07:20.630
And boom, if that person was
black, or Muslim, or Asian not

00:07:20.630 --> 00:07:22.760
too long ago, the
odds that they were

00:07:22.760 --> 00:07:25.370
going to get that opportunity
to execute that black trade

00:07:25.370 --> 00:07:29.630
would have been
smaller than otherwise.

00:07:29.630 --> 00:07:30.620
The world is changing.

00:07:30.620 --> 00:07:31.990
The world has changed.

00:07:31.990 --> 00:07:34.520
We can be very grateful for
all that's occurring around us,

00:07:34.520 --> 00:07:38.540
but we want to be able to ensure
that we have excellent people

00:07:38.540 --> 00:07:40.370
in place well-trained--

00:07:40.370 --> 00:07:45.500
trained to not just survive in
these environments, but thrive.

00:07:45.500 --> 00:07:48.510
And if we've done our job well,
the next time that block trade

00:07:48.510 --> 00:07:50.910
or that big project
whatever comes up,

00:07:50.910 --> 00:07:53.150
it's going to be fair play
to everyone in the room,

00:07:53.150 --> 00:07:57.470
because everyone is shown to
have proven their worth, proven

00:07:57.470 --> 00:08:01.070
their ability, and if
we've done our job well,

00:08:01.070 --> 00:08:04.540
we'll have been a part of that
success and that training.

00:08:04.540 --> 00:08:06.260
You want jump in here?

00:08:06.260 --> 00:08:08.270
We have a virtuous cycle.

00:08:08.270 --> 00:08:11.330
We go out and take
sponsorship donations

00:08:11.330 --> 00:08:13.732
from large corporates
like a Google.

00:08:13.732 --> 00:08:15.440
And we go into the
world and we go to all

00:08:15.440 --> 00:08:16.700
the different universities.

00:08:16.700 --> 00:08:18.260
We bring together
an applicant pool.

00:08:18.260 --> 00:08:18.950
We screen them.

00:08:18.950 --> 00:08:19.430
We scrub them.

00:08:19.430 --> 00:08:20.055
They sort them.

00:08:20.055 --> 00:08:20.870
We sift system.

00:08:20.870 --> 00:08:22.970
We decide who do we think
in this group can most

00:08:22.970 --> 00:08:28.370
benefit from our help,
but also, if we help them,

00:08:28.370 --> 00:08:30.110
will go really, really far?

00:08:30.110 --> 00:08:31.699
And those are sort
of the two drivers.

00:08:31.699 --> 00:08:33.860
And who do we think
if we assist will

00:08:33.860 --> 00:08:38.630
be able to then draw a
community behind them to sort

00:08:38.630 --> 00:08:42.980
of really embed through their
hard work, dedication, success,

00:08:42.980 --> 00:08:48.800
and applied talent you know,
a change for all concerned,

00:08:48.800 --> 00:08:50.450
the firms that are
sponsoring them,

00:08:50.450 --> 00:08:53.450
the people coming
in behind them.

00:08:53.450 --> 00:08:55.030
So we find folks.

00:08:55.030 --> 00:08:56.940
We try and create
lasting outcomes.

00:08:56.940 --> 00:08:59.340
And again, it's not about you.

00:08:59.340 --> 00:09:01.310
It's about the people
coming after you.

00:09:01.310 --> 00:09:02.880
We want people to
be giving back.

