they're going to make it--

00:09:06.796 --> 00:09:07.740
it's all about them.

00:09:07.740 --> 00:09:09.380
It's all about
their own success,

00:09:09.380 --> 00:09:11.270
and they're master
of their own domain.

00:09:11.270 --> 00:09:12.410
Useless.

00:09:12.410 --> 00:09:14.900
That is not someone who's
going to help our organization

00:09:14.900 --> 00:09:15.964
