two or three other careers,

00:14:15.040 --> 00:14:17.660
alumni from The New York
program launched in China--

00:14:17.660 --> 00:14:22.036
Hong Kong and Shanghai,
then in Saigon, Ho Chi Minh,

00:14:22.036 --> 00:14:24.310
we have a SEO Vietnam.

00:14:24.310 --> 00:14:25.660
We launched a scholars program.

00:14:25.660 --> 00:14:27.730
Just as in New
York, they started

00:14:27.730 --> 00:14:31.174
with secondary schoolers and
went to sort of university,

00:14:31.174 --> 00:14:33.590
we started with the university,
and we were doing so well.

00:14:33.590 --> 00:14:36.217
We were seeing such great growth
and such a robust response

00:14:36.217 --> 00:14:38.550
from the community that we
started our scholars program.

00:14:38.550 --> 00:14:40.090
We were backwards.

00:14:40.090 --> 00:14:42.970
And we've since then launched
our Connect Program, which

00:14:42.970 --> 00:14:45.220
I described earlier, and
we have a program in Accra,

00:14:45.220 --> 00:14:49.510
in Ghana, which is actively
looking at Lagos in Nigeria

00:14:49.510 --> 00:14:52.000
as a potential expansion point.

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:52.660
It goes on.

00:14:52.660 --> 00:14:55.180
I've been involved in
discussions about SEO Bogota.

00:14:55.180 --> 00:14:58.690
I've been involved in
SEO Rio and Sao Paolo.

00:14:58.690 --> 00:15:01.150
And one of our staffers
is from Afghanistan.

00:15:01.150 --> 00:15:02.410
He was going back to Kabul.

00:15:02.410 --> 00:15:03.620
I was only half
joking when I said,

00:15:03.620 --> 00:15:05.369
we should be talking
about SEO Kabul, man,

00:15:05.369 --> 00:15:08.520
because it's a universal
concept that there

00:15:08.520 --> 00:15:11.230
are those who have access and
those that do not have access.

00:15:11.230 --> 00:15:14.280
And it is, to my mind,
is a clear statement

00:15:14.280 --> 00:15:16.890
to say that there is money
being left on the table

00:15:16.890 --> 00:15:18.400
with everyone's not involved.

00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:21.870
And so my sense is that we have
an opportunity to do more here.

00:15:21.870 --> 00:15:24.870
