some organization looking

00:16:06.160 --> 00:16:07.900
to learn more about what
we do because they're

00:16:07.900 --> 00:16:09.970
trying to embed more
diversity and inclusiveness

00:16:09.970 --> 00:16:10.780
in their culture.

00:16:10.780 --> 00:16:12.390
That's fantastic.

00:16:12.390 --> 00:16:13.611
That's absolutely fantastic.

00:16:13.611 --> 00:16:14.110
I'm here.

00:16:14.110 --> 00:16:15.360
You guys are talking about it.

00:16:17.730 --> 00:16:19.832
We're in a really
interesting place.

00:16:19.832 --> 00:16:21.790
I just sort of sit back
and do a little victory

00:16:21.790 --> 00:16:24.290
dance every time I hear about
some new program that's coming

00:16:24.290 --> 00:16:26.020
up, because we're a charity.

00:16:26.020 --> 00:16:28.390
No one is getting
rich off of this.

00:16:28.390 --> 00:16:30.100
What we care about
is the social change,

00:16:30.100 --> 00:16:31.314
the long term impact of this.

00:16:31.314 --> 00:16:32.980
And we see that
happening all around us.

