The city of London is
radically different, completely

00:16:40.720 --> 00:16:42.459
different than
what it was before.

00:16:42.459 --> 00:16:44.500
There's still lots of
people trying to clambering

00:16:44.500 --> 00:16:47.680
and getting into jobs.

00:16:47.680 --> 00:16:50.150
Lots of ground
still yet to cover.

00:16:50.150 --> 00:16:53.620
But let me tell you, 2000,
this wasn't even a thing.

